 121:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   * @brief  USBH_Get_CfgDesc
 122:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   *         Issues Configuration Descriptor to the device. Once the response
 123:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   *         received, it parses the configuration descriptor and updates the
 124:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   *         status.
