 154:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   * @brief  USBH_Get_StringDesc
 155:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   *         Issues string Descriptor command to the device. Once the response
